# Input

```grit
`console.$method('$message');` => `console.warn('$message');` where {
  or { $message <: "Hello, world!", $method <: `error` }
}

```


# Formatted

```grit
`console.$method('$message');` => `console.warn('$message');` where {
	or { $message <: "Hello, world!", $method <: `error` }
}

```
